snippet.title: Jumpala Trailer - Now on itch.io!
snippet.description:
=== Now available on itch.io! https://yokereba.itch.io/jumpala ===

Here's the first trailer for #Jumpala, a competitive multiplayer platformer for up to 4 players!

This trailer also introduces a brand new character, Bommer!

=====
Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/YokerebaGames
=====
This game is a work in progress. Assets, characters, names, and gameplay mechanics may change as development continues. Thanks for understanding!
